snippet.textDisplay: Here's a fun thing to try: Get a long PVC tube (about 2 metres long and with a diameter of 1-2 inches) with a 90 degree bend in the end. Put about 5 inches of pipe on the other side of the 90-degree bend, and put a little methylated spirits  (maybe rubbing alcohol will work too) and let it evaporate like you do a whoosh bottle. Then ignite the longer end and it will make not only the coolest noise but also a huge flame! Ps. DON"T TRY THIS AT HOME!
